divs: Sighting DetailsSmall bright orb traveling from left to right, passed under a star. Quickly turned up then seemed to get faster and traveled out of sight as if it was rapidly acsending into deep space. Three of us were outside looking for it, where we usually see it. It appeared after about 15 minutes in a direction a pattern we havent seen before. It was visible for about a minute. We went out several times after that had not seen it. Its been getting the attention of many people in the neighborhood.
